name: Bang Jana
description: Bang Jana (Bro Jana), a white bear from Cilandak Town Square, South Jakarta whose name is short for Sarjana because previously he wore a toga robe complete with his hat. At first, Bang Jana was known as an academic and genius figure. However, one day he experienced an accident in the washing machine in Thamrin area which caused his hat to come off and made Jana's attitude change 180 degrees he finally decided to take off his undergraduate attributes, even though he was still called Bang Jana until now.
